Create a repository on AWS
You can decide to create a user with ECR permission assigned to generate Secrete and Access key
On your ec2 instande, run AWS configure
Use the Access and Secrete key of the user you created
Then, on AWS repository you created, click the Repository name, which takes you inside the Repository
Click the "View Push Command" button on the top right of the page you are.
Follow the steps one after the other. It is very straightforward!
